body:
What I&#039;m looking for is a player capable of playing both roles rather well, preferably have some strong picks whether they are meta or not. If you can show dominance on your pick it will greatly help the picks we can choose. The rank is between P3 - D4. The end goal is to be able to swap 2 players with strong picks around the mid and top to confuse and mind game the enemy. The team is part of a league so you will get weekly games, I just ask that you show up to those games and practice with the team once a week. If you are interested add me on League.

Also, the style I hope to achieve with this team is a 1-4 or 1-3-1. So this is for all of those of you that like to split, not to discredit tank players because you are valuable in the 1-4s.

